    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p><code>@RestController</code> is composition of <code>@Controller</code> and <code>@ResponseBody</code>, if we are not using the <code>@ResponseBody</code> in Method signature then we need to use the <code>@Restcontroller</code>.</p>\n"
  }, {
