    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>THE new @RestController annotation in Spring4+, which marks the class as a controller where every method returns a domain object instead of a view. It’s shorthand for @Controller and @ResponseBody rolled together.</p>\n"
