    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 3,
    "last_activity_date" : 1608375497,
    "last_edit_date" : 1608375497,
    "creation_date" : 1576483059,
    "answer_id" : 59352488,
    "question_id" : 25242321,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p><code>@Controller</code> is used in legacy systems which use JSPs. it can return views.\n<code>@RestController</code> is to mark the controller is providing REST services with JSON response type. so it wraps <code>@Controller</code> and <code>@ResponseBody</code> annotations together.</p>\n"
