    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>The @Controller annotation indicates that the class is a &quot;Controller&quot; like a web controller while @RestController annotation indicates that the class is a controller where @RequestMapping methods assume @ResponseBody semantics by default i.e. servicing REST API</p>\n"
