    "body" : "<p><code>@RestController</code> is the combination of <code>@Controller</code> and <code>@ResponseBody</code>.</p>\n<p>Flow of request in a <code>@Controller</code> class without using a <code>@ResponseBody</code> annotation:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/xm7KW.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/xm7KW.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n<p><code>@RestController</code> returns an object as response instead of view.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/wCZrD.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/wCZrD.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n"
